ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The course looks at popular culture in Moscow in the beginning of the 20th century (before 1917) trying to explore everyday life of a Muscovite. It looks at many different kinds of cultural production: theater, cinema, amusement gardens; travelogues, memoirs and etc. Recommended to anyone who would like an unconventional look at Russian culture or anyone interested in Moscow in particular.
